oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bluebird 78's - tape 4
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Tape 4 of recordings of Bluebird 78 discs, featuring Thibodeaux Boys (performers), Jean Fuselier (performer), Joe's Arcadians (performers), The Four Aces (performers), and Hackberry Ramblers (performers), performing Creole tunes from the 1930's.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Thibodeaux Boys; Jean Fuselier; Joe's Acadians; The Four Aces; Hackberry Ramblers
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Test tones -- La Two Step A Erbie (Thibodeaux Boys) -- Redell Breakdown (Jean Fuselier) -- Ma Cher Bassett (Jean Fuselier) -- La Valse A Deux Temps (Joe's Arcadians) -- Vals De Rebot (Jean Fuselier) -- Ponce A Moi (Jean Fuselier) -- Je Vous Jaime Kate (The Four Aces) -- Leleux Breakdown (The Four Aces) -- French Two Step (Hackberry Ramblers) -- Si Tu Voudroit Marriez Avec Moi (Joe's Arcadians)
